{"tid":1920064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主黨要求臨時撥款議案刪除特首辦及警務處的撥款","createTime":"2020-03-11T08:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T08:10:16.000Z","uid":250449,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95d4948120839271deebcf233414cb628f92ab07","tid":1920064,"uid":250449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:09:01.000Z","msg":"政府下星期三將根據公共財務條例，向立法會提出決議案，要求撥款約2150億元，即是大約新年度政府開支的兩成，以應付預算案未通過前，政府在四月一日開始的新年度開支。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨表示，會要求在這筆臨時撥款中，刪除特首辦及警務處的開支，民主黨批評，行政長官林鄭月娥過去大半年，面對社會運動及現時的疫情，均漠視民意，認為特首辦沒資格獲得撥款，另外，若臨時撥款通過，亦擔心警務處會用作購買裝甲車及水炮車等裝備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272986&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1272986%26csid%3D261_341&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stotKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=d8aafc19\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1272986&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"201b3dd0132aef0f07ff4016ca7ea0bfaa625e66","tid":1920064,"uid":64337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:09:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b83f164be1f051157fac8f2908c23596d0d0a50a","tid":1920064,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T08:10:16.000Z","msg":"今次反應又幾快窩"}]}